OL,5, The cast of The Lords of the Rings have
OL,6, paid tribute to their co-star Bernard  
OL,7, Hill, who has died aged 79.            
OL,9,FThe actor - who played King Theoden in 
OL,10,FPeter Jackson's trilogy - passed away  
OL,11,Fearly on Sunday morning.               
OL,13,FElijah Wood, Billy Boyd, Dominic       
OL,14,FMonaghan and Sean Astin, who played the
OL,15,Ffour Hobbits in the films, said goodbye
OL,16,Fto their "funny, gruff, beautiful"     
OL,17,Ffriend.                                
OL,19,FThey told Comic Con fans in Liverpool  
OL,20,Fthey had lost a "family member".       
